SerialDataCMOSBits              * 7:SHL:5
                                        ; Bit  0   = AutoDST
                                        ;                     0 = manual DST changes
                                        ;                     1 = DST changes handled automatically by territory module
                                        ; Bit  1   = speaker volume
                                        ;                     0 = Quiet
                                        ;                     1 = Loud
